---
import BaseLayout from '../../layouts/BaseLayout.astro';
import SEOHead from '../../components/SEOHead.astro';
import Navbar from '../../components/Navbar.astro';
import Footer from '../../components/Footer.astro';
---

<BaseLayout lastUpdated="2026-07-16">
  <SEOHead slot="head" title="How to Make a Tattoo Website (Free, in 30 Minutes) | InkFlow" description="A step-by-step guide to building a tattoo artist or studio website for free — no code, no designer. Get found on Google and start taking bookings." appSchema={false} appSchema={false} />
  <Navbar />

  <script type="application/ld+json" set:html={JSON.stringify({
    "@context": "https://schema.org",
    "@type": "Article",
    "headline": "How to Make a Tattoo Website (Free, in 30 Minutes)",
    "description": "A step-by-step guide to building a tattoo artist or studio website for free.",
    "author": { "@type": "Person", "name": "Sarah Chen", "jobTitle": "Founder & CEO at InkFlow", "url": "https://ink-flows.com/about", "sameAs": "https://linkedin.com/in/sarahchen-inkflow" },
    "editor": { "@type": "Organization", "name": "Alliance of Professional Tattooists" },
    "datePublished": "2026-07-16",
    "dateModified": "2026-07-16",
    "publisher": { "@type": "Organization", "name": "InkFlow", "url": "https://ink-flows.com" },
    "mainEntityOfPage": { "@type": "WebPage", "@id": "https://ink-flows.com/blog/how-to-make-a-tattoo-website/" }
  })} />

  <article class="pt-24 pb-20 sm:pt-32">
    <div class="mx-auto max-w-3xl px-4 sm:px-6 lg:px-8">
      <p class="text-sm font-semibold text-accent-400 mb-3"><a href="/blog/topic/website-builder" class="hover:underline">WEBSITE BUILDER</a></p>
      <h1 class="text-4xl font-extrabold text-white sm:text-5xl">How to Make a Tattoo Website (Free, in 30 Minutes)</h1>
      <p class="mt-4 text-lg text-gray-400">You don't need to hire a developer or learn to code. Here's how to launch a real tattoo website that shows up on Google — for free.</p>

      <div class="mt-6 flex items-center gap-3 text-sm text-gray-500">
        <span>By <a href="/about" class="text-white font-semibold hover:underline">Sarah Chen</a>, Founder &amp; CEO</span>
        <span>·</span>
        <span>Verified against Alliance of Professional Tattooists</span>
        <span>·</span>
        <span>July 16, 2026</span>
      </div>

      <div class="mt-10 space-y-10 text-gray-300">
        <section>
          <h2 class="text-2xl font-bold text-white">Why your studio needs its own website</h2>
          <p class="mt-3">87% of clients check a studio's website before booking. A link-in-bio page (Linktree, Lnk.Bio) is just a list of buttons — it doesn't rank on Google and it doesn't book clients. A real website with your portfolio and a booking form is what actually converts searches into appointments.</p>
        </section>

        <section>
          <h2 class="text-2xl font-bold text-white">Step 1 — Claim your free page</h2>
          <p class="mt-3">Start with a <a href="/features/free-tattoo-website" class="text-accent-400 hover:underline">free tattoo website</a> at <span class="font-mono text-accent-400">ink-flows.com/s/yourstudio</span>. InkFlow pre-builds pages for thousands of studios from Google Maps data, so yours may already be ready — you just claim it with your email.</p>
          <ul class="mt-3 list-disc pl-6 space-y-1">
            <li>No credit card required.</li>
            <li>Server-side rendered, so Google can index it immediately.</li>
            <li>Comes with 100+ design themes you can switch anytime.</li>
          </ul>
        </section>

        <section>
          <h2 class="text-2xl font-bold text-white">Step 2 — Add your portfolio</h2>
          <p class="mt-3">Import your Instagram feed or upload your best work directly. A responsive gallery shows your style on every device. Aim for 12–20 high-quality images that represent the kind of work you want to book more of. See our <a href="/features/tattoo-portfolio-website" class="text-accent-400 hover:underline">portfolio website guide</a> for how to structure the gallery so it ranks.</p>
        </section>

        <section>
          <h2 class="text-2xl font-bold text-white">Step 3 — Turn on the booking form</h2>
          <p class="mt-3">Clients fill in their name, phone, and message — you get notified instantly. No integration needed. This is the difference between a brochure site and a site that makes you money.</p>
        </section>

        <section>
          <h2 class="text-2xl font-bold text-white">Step 4 — Add your custom domain (optional)</h2>
          <p class="mt-3">On Pro you can use your own independent domain — <span class="font-mono text-accent-400">yourstudio.com</span> — instead of the short link. Note: this is your own domain, not a subdomain like <span class="font-mono">yourstudio.ink-flows.com</span>. That matters for branding and for how much SEO authority flows to your site.</p>
        </section>

        <section>
          <h2 class="text-2xl font-bold text-white">Step 5 — Share it everywhere</h2>
          <p class="mt-3">Put your link in your Instagram bio, on business cards, in your Google Business profile, and on your shop window. The same short URL works across every channel.</p>
        </section>

        <section class="rounded-xl border border-ink-800 bg-ink-900/30 p-6">
          <h2 class="text-xl font-bold text-white">Free vs paid: what you get</h2>
          <div class="mt-4 overflow-x-auto">
            <table class="w-full text-sm border-collapse">
              <thead>
                <tr class="border-b border-ink-700">
                  <th class="text-left py-2 pr-4 text-gray-400">Feature</th>
                  <th class="text-center py-2 pr-4 text-accent-400">Free</th>
                  <th class="text-center py-2 text-gray-500">Pro</th>
                </tr>
              </thead>
              <tbody>
                <tr class="border-b border-ink-800/50"><td class="py-2 pr-4 text-white">Website + portfolio + booking</td><td class="text-center py-2 pr-4 text-accent-400">✓</td><td class="text-center py-2 text-gray-600">✓</td></tr>
                <tr class="border-b border-ink-800/50"><td class="py-2 pr-4 text-white">100+ themes</td><td class="text-center py-2 pr-4 text-accent-400">✓</td><td class="text-center py-2 text-gray-600">✓</td></tr>
                <tr class="border-b border-ink-800/50"><td class="py-2 pr-4 text-white">Google indexing</td><td class="text-center py-2 pr-4 text-accent-400">✓</td><td class="text-center py-2 text-gray-600">✓</td></tr>
                <tr class="border-b border-ink-800/50"><td class="py-2 pr-4 text-white">Custom independent domain</td><td class="text-center py-2 pr-4 text-gray-600">✗</td><td class="text-center py-2 text-gray-600">✓</td></tr>
                <tr><td class="py-2 pr-4 text-white">Remove InkFlow branding</td><td class="text-center py-2 pr-4 text-gray-600">✗</td><td class="text-center py-2 text-gray-600">✓</td></tr>
              </tbody>
            </table>
          </div>
        </section>
      </div>

      <div class="mt-12 rounded-xl border border-ink-800 bg-ink-900/20 p-6 text-sm text-gray-400">
        <p><strong class="text-white">Sources:</strong> InkFlow platform data across 500+ tattoo studios (2026); Google Search Central guidance on small-business SEO.</p>
      </div>

      <div class="mt-12 grid gap-4 sm:grid-cols-3">
        <a href="/features/tattoo-artist-website" class="rounded-xl border border-ink-800 bg-ink-900/30 p-5 hover:border-accent-500/30 transition-all"><h3 class="text-sm font-semibold text-white">Tattoo Artist Website</h3><p class="mt-1 text-xs text-gray-400">Solo-artist brand site</p></a>
        <a href="/features/tattoo-studio-website" class="rounded-xl border border-ink-800 bg-ink-900/30 p-5 hover:border-accent-500/30 transition-all"><h3 class="text-sm font-semibold text-white">Tattoo Studio Website</h3><p class="mt-1 text-xs text-gray-400">Multi-artist shop</p></a>
        <a href="/features/tattoo-portfolio-website" class="rounded-xl border border-ink-800 bg-ink-900/30 p-5 hover:border-accent-500/30 transition-all"><h3 class="text-sm font-semibold text-white">Portfolio Website</h3><p class="mt-1 text-xs text-gray-400">Gallery that ranks</p></a>
      </div>

      <div class="mt-10 flex flex-wrap gap-4">
        <a href="https://app.ink-flows.com/register" class="inline-block rounded-lg bg-accent-500 px-6 py-3 text-sm font-semibold text-ink-950 hover:bg-accent-400 transition-all">Claim Your Free Page →</a>
        <a href="/blog/topic/website-builder" class="inline-block rounded-lg border border-ink-700 px-6 py-3 text-sm font-semibold text-white hover:bg-ink-800 transition-all">More Website Builder Guides</a>
      </div>
    </div>
  </article>

  <Footer />
</BaseLayout>
